Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw a shooting star the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Kagami said something about the wishing three times thing being unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shooting stars are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult to see the stars from our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Since your house is in the city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I would probably be too amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...to have time to make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The sight of a dazzling, shining star...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...would fill you with feelings of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That could explain the myth that shooting stars grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your honesty is what dazzles me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have finals first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans for winter break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't taken a vacation in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Asakusa the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how you get sleepy on the train during winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She missed her stop!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't that in the opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The train reached the end of the line and turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I missed my stop again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I was conscious, we were in Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only miss your stop so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't entirely a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I hadn't visited Asakusa in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't be doing that right before finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:03:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had a feeling I saw a girl in a sailor uniform with a machine gun walk by...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me someone was making a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeping more helps you grow more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're growing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got an even better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad pulled an all-nighter and then went to turn in a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He got on an early-morning train but missed his stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then it reached the end and made a U-turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so when he woke up, he'd already missed his stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this happened a few more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He started to wake up when he got close to his station,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.22,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Patrasche...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but he still ended up missing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.72,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He was tired and wanted to get home and sleep, but he couldn't get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he no longer knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...which direction he was going whenever he woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I still wake up before my stop when I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she has an internal alarm clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, it doesn't work all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she's always snacking away. {dat bleed - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But train seats are really warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so you get really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all warm and fuzzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...like you're sitting next to the window in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...on a sunny winter afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Covering for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I tried to wake you up on the ride home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just five more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She yelled out half-asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone around us was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my friends did that in class once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Birds of a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're grouping us together!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But why five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you went to wake someone up and they were, like, "Give me another hour!"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't you be pissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...but five minutes comes up in a lot of other situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, just wait five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe 'cause it isn't too long or too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, the five-minute wait for a train feels really long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,People who say to wait five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...tend to make you wait a lot longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how people say to not use your cell or put on makeup on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a lot worse when the person next to you leans on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you end up wanting to stand after managing to get a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you're stuck with the sticky head of an old person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I try to shove them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they somehow manage to keep returning to the same position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When I fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and there's a man on one side and an empty seat on the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...I try to lean myself towards the empty seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...but for some reason, I always end up leaning the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess your body feels more comfortable leaning a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see someone leaning over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...I shrink up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...then their elbow hits my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean they're actually awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...some people at our school take the inbound train home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and some people take the outbound train home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. {added - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't the ones who take the inbound train look more refined somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Yuki-chan's an inbounder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to the farm, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the stop before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get any studying done yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually put in a lot of effort this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How much studying did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.14,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HC97F96&}Only four hours. {choose and alt? - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HB06E45&}A whole four hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at everything, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do a lot of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're definitely really competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's my pride as the other sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have to be ahead of Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, I usually say neither of us is really older or younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be pretty worried about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tsukasa probably wasn't much competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Kona-chan thinks she's all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what my present will be this year. {She is getting only one present? ;__;}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You still get presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How long did you believe in Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus isn't real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.50,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa never came to Konata's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...so her dad gave her presents in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she thought he might be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He really wants to look good in front of his daughter, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the handout from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, Hiiragi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped your pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the handout from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sebastian, like, stinks. {"Like" really necessary?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.36,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I go to Tsukasa's class a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My cavity started hurting recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't stand dentists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to see the dentist for your cavity the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dentists take a long time on each tooth,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have to repeat the procedure for every tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...so it takes a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ended up escaping...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...after making a number of excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She sounded all cutesy... {Use "cute" or "adorable" instead of "cutesy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that's pretty crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go wild with everyone on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have plans for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Dad that I'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really going on a date with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm just working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost all the customers are male, so I wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought you'd managed to get ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a special event on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We dress like Santa Claus for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You really love that kind of stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys also cosplay as shrine maidens for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At your temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call it cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good that Santa-san gives everyone presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...but ever since I was little, I was like, "He's totally trespassing."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't look down on something based on a holy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiteful brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa is supposed to give children dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's with the men who turn to this squirt with their dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You just casually insulted a lot of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it okay for you guys to celebrate Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We usually get Christmas presents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We worship every god there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We regularly visit temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we sang in a church choir once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:55.88,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:11:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A shrine maiden said she wanted to get married in a wedding dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that be a little complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting chilly these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That man's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something odd about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing odd at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with you. {time is short, line is long - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why cops are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a cop yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does someone have to call now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're about to reveal the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. {serious business here - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the killer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No use in hiding it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why these two-hour shows always end on the edge of a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe 'cause people aren't willing to act until their back's against a wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san, evenin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha watchin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A movie for a popular detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Crimes don't happen in conference rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They happen at the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever gets that passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you reject that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...the receipts were stolen at the behest of the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why he fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They eat pork bowls a lot in police shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...but apparently, that isn't actually allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's fiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...so a lot of it is probably made-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So police commissioner's granddaughters aren't really like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Police commissioner's granddaughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never met one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd at least want Mai-chan to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To give me hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Empty dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of cases with adults going after children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you teach kids martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't there be a decrease in that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After intensive training...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...Oyama-sensei was able to beat a cow with his bare hands, with one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And bears toppled like trees after a couple of hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But won't that come back to haunt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When those kids grow up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...the adults will be strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,People say that training in the martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...helps you mature as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone who does martial arts and hasn't matured right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. {where? - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this cousin, Yui-neesan's little sister, who's entering high school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She's physically weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she's sweet and pure and really adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.10,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Konata-neesan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I start thinking about how a healthy spirit leads to a healthy body,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I start feeling like something dark is lurking behind those shining eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt aphorisms are universal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The year's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's December, you always feel like the year flew by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to help out at your temple as shrine maidens again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come draw your fortune again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With fortunes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get really bad luck, it's an unpleasant feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you get really good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...it feels like you already wasted your luck for the year, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why people say average luck is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then here's an early present from your Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your report cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:36.34,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Here! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want this present!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We give presents based on effort in my school of Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Think on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a bonus to your winter homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of Christmas cakes will be good this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go to a bakery...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...there are so many cute cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you can have fun just by looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to the cakes that weren't sold before Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the employees take them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But if nobody takes them, they might throw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They often compare marriage to Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, how twenty-five is the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're past twenty-five, a Christmas cake is just another cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After one night, it's just another decorated cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...that suddenly looks stale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...so you lose your appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about Santa-san with Kona-chan the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How long did you believe in Santa, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like you would have been a true believer like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I also believed in Santa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was little, I tried to send a letter of gratitude to Santa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...and did some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't learn much after asking my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I did some thorough investigating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and learned of the people Santa Claus was based on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and once I saw the phrase "origin of Santa Claus" pop up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...my dreams were quickly shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you do, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what you would expect from Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never do so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a little pissed about losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan's at the top of our class so it's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We could never beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...but stuff like bust size...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a cup of ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,These three minutes of waiting feel really long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this to kill time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And then your noodles end up soggy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The extra broth for my cup fried soba dried up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me she would be late...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let her make a habit of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to give her a stern dressing down every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As the man of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What time do you think it i-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Christmas present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been cold outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some hot tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I do! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,G'day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-neesan's here to save the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.30,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,You stink of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous to DUI!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I parked the car somewhere and had a drink nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Christmas Eve, yet my husband's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plans tonight are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.79,0:17:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you go to your parents' place instead every once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to sneak in and surprise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you at your parents' place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Running every light on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, you shouldn't be breaking the law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll log in for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't a leftover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't count as a leftover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I bought one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was here last Sunday to buy manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get why you pay the fare to come here so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's for the points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is pretty excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really love this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, do you even use the prizes they give?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't. {added "No" - Flyer}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of stuff is hard to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Their value would go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get shocked by static electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Konata's always sitting in front of the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so her body's already full of weird waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I really can't stand winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.99,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And I heard you can get shocked just by touching someone's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you two don't really hate each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:12.79,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.58,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:14.32,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:14.98,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:15.87,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanted to try it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your navigator, Kogami Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already on the eleventh episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And on this eleventh episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have some wonderful news you've all been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's sent in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.64,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,She's really in it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...lots of passionate letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...asking for Akira to show up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:57.86,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode, I, Kogami Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.43,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm the assistant, Shiraishi Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be showing up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,But I need to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you to Izumi Konata from Saitama along with everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...who sent postcards to Newtype!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So Akira-sama's also making an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Like, you're finally showing up in the twelfth episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in it for, like, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho. Ho. Ho."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...attitude you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to appear with Akira-sama in the actual show as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All you did this week was pick up a handkerchief, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be thinking you've got what it takes to make it in this business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that you can just disappear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After that announcement...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.73,0:20:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...you can't wait for the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You want it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is probably trembling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, shaking naked in their boots in anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We should treat our fans with care...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...and air it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We could grab a thirty minute slot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.55,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:01.23,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That'd be pushing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Or forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So send any messages to the radio show or the home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:09.40,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if I overshadowed the main characters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It would indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a tendency for the main character's friends and rivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...to end up more popular than the actual main characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...talking about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so full of yourself 'cause you're popular lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.09,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect this to last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.54,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,No, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be placing first in the poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.85,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.14,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.14,0:21:38.80,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Listen to m-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, we have a duet from Tsukasa and Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go up front to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose a song for them to sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all kinds of songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still an anime song, isn't it?
