Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.85,0:23:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really hungry one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.44,0:23:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it was really late...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I was wondering if I should eat something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally decided a little bite would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I went to the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I remembered I had some snacks left over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.86,0:23:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I opened up the freezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.08,0:23:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already out of time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's Go to the Festival."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to next time!
